Package: SigAssignR
Title: Assign COSMIC signatures to mutation matrix using NNLS 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Nuri/Alpay", "Temiz", , "temizna@umn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Assign COSMIC signatures to mutation matrix using NNLS. A mutation matrix can be created using MutationalPatterns or mutmat_nonvcf function. The assigned signatures can be plotted with plot_sigs. APOBEC enrichment is calculated by first using vcf_to_inputdata for vcffiles or read_nonvcf for non-vcf files to create the required dataframe format and then by using apobec_enrichment function. 
Depends:
	nnls(>= 1.4),
	sigminer(>= 2.2.2),
	ggplot2(>= 3.4.2),
	stringr(>=1.5.0)
